    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 双人大逃脱 – How 2 Escape 密室逃脱两个人玩用脑子的，一个用手机一个用电脑，游戏只能通过不同的媒介然后合作才能完成，无需网络链接</h2> 。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264140/extras/68641f584e40fd104443a67a0ee03ba9.avif?t=1751497531\" width=600 height=94 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264140/extras/f74e9add1f6ca009c32ddb6a6a94a8b0.poster.avif?t=1751497531\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264140/extras/f74e9add1f6ca009c32ddb6a6a94a8b0.webm?t=1751497531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264140/extras/f74e9add1f6ca009c32ddb6a6a94a8b0.mp4?t=1751497531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>  <br>双人大逃脱 – How 2 Escape 是一款需要两名玩家在不同游戏设备上进行合作的双人解谜游戏，一人使用PC或主机端的游戏本体，另一人用手机或PC下载免费的APP来协助解谜。这是一款值得你和家人或室友共同度过几个小时的社交型解谜游戏，推荐给希望和他人进行交流的玩家们尝试。<br><br>*在iOs和Android上获取免费的How 2 Escape同伴应用程序。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264140/extras/cd4838fa47058e63e68124d0e7fb5cb8.avif?t=1751497531\" width=600 height=94 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264140/extras/fffe3ca0afe5fc361028db9fb6e41c76.poster.avif?t=1751497531\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264140/extras/fffe3ca0afe5fc361028db9fb6e41c76.webm?t=1751497531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264140/extras/fffe3ca0afe5fc361028db9fb6e41c76.mp4?t=1751497531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>一款极度硬核的解谜游戏，涉及摩斯密码，音乐旋律，化学方程式，数学，英语，逻辑推导，做菜，数独，电路图等。最重要的是这是一款需要俩人重度沟通的游戏，两个人的设备不同，画面不同，但揭开对方谜题的答案就埋藏在自己的游戏环境当中。<br>建议朋友们叫上自己的好兄弟通过这个游戏来检测一下你们的默契程度。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264140/extras/30882c7466bc6b43e37aba990901e57a.avif?t=1751497531\" width=600 height=94 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264140/extras/cfedab33dd46d2fc297e0197b3f1193b.poster.avif?t=1751497531\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264140/extras/cfedab33dd46d2fc297e0197b3f1193b.webm?t=1751497531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2264140/extras/cfedab33dd46d2fc297e0197b3f1193b.mp4?t=1751497531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>埃米醒来时，发现自己被困在一辆高速行驶的火车上，火车内布满了陷阱和神秘的谜题。她唯一的出路是抵达机车的刹车杆，以停止火车。而埃米的兄弟约翰则在电话的另一端，拥有能帮助埃米在各个车厢中导航并逃离火车的关键信息。你能及时拯救埃米吗？",
